welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Youngsville, where southern charm meets modern amenities. Known for its picturesque landscapes and friendly community, we invite you to discover all that our city has to offer and make unforgettable memories during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lafayette Regional Airport houses all arrival and departure gates.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Lafayette Regional Airport is primarily used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free wifi network for internet access.
